data.description: Welcome home! Now available, two bed, two bath, two car attached garage townhome in The Lakes Area of Blaine. Main level features a private outdoor patio, living room, dining room and kitchen with ample cabinet and counter space, center island with granite counter top, under cabinet lighting and stainless steel appliances. Upper level features a large loft area, closet washer and dryer, owners suite with walk-in closet and large walk-through bathroom. Fantastic area of Blaine and is close to many recreational trails, shopping, dining and more!
